%^RESET%^%^BOLD%^%^GREEN%^Prestige Class
%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Warmind:

%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Requirements:
%^RESET%^ Level 20 Psywarrior
%^RESET%^ 20 Base Intelligence (before equipment modifiers)

%^RESET%^%^CYAN%^Class Feats:%^RESET%^
 %^RESET%^L1: flawless control
 %^RESET%^L4: mind over matter
 %^RESET%^L7: battle psyche

Warminds have mastered their awareness of the matter around them. They are completely in tune with their own bodies and can makeminute changes to their cells, boosting their performance. Thisawareness extends to the world around them, helping them to innately understand the physical realm. Warminds are able to flawlessly shape their powers so that they do not harm membersof their own parties. They are also able to manipulate their ownbodies so that their wounds heal themselves. Because of theirdedication to perfecting their own bodies, warminds receivea +2 on all endurance and athletics checks.

